Program: The Forum
Title: Core: A Journey to the Centre of the Earth
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p036vvz4
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 11 Nov 2015
How startling discoveries about the core of the earth and the oldest star yet known help us understand our place in the grand scheme of things. Tim Marlow and the astrophysicist Arif Babul, the astronomer Anna Frebel and the earth scientist Paul Savage go on a quest to find the core or centre. (Photo: a split Earth showing a molten core) Show less